claim.claim-text:
10. The method of claim 1, wherein the second web of film comprises a plurality of deposition mask patterns, and said method further comprises:
positioning the second web of film comprises a plurality of deposition mask patterns over the first area of the first web of film;
depositing additional material on at least a portion of the first area of the first web of film through a deposition mask pattern defined by the second web of film to create another portion of the integrated circuit;
repeating said positioning and depositing steps one or more times, wherein the additional material comprises inorganic semiconductor material, organic semiconductor material, dielectric material, conductive material, amorphous silicon, pentacene, or a combination thereof.
